I lost a poker game to my girlfriend
column3: and the wager was that I wouldn't play video games for the rest of the year. Admittedly
column4: I found myself surprisingly eager for the new year to arrive so I could indulge in meaningful games
column5: particularly Final Fantasy X. As soon as I could
column8: I encountered a beautiful shot. It's a fleeting moment
column11: the soon-to-be best friend of the protagonist
column12: playfully pushes the hesitant hero into a lake
column13: then looks on to ensure he's okay. In that instant
column14: I felt compelled to capture and convey the essence of the game visually with just that single screenshot. The result is this manipulated image
column15: which I believe captures the essence of Final Fantasy X quite nicely."
